OL,3,CGovernment faces criminal charges over
OL,4,Cexplosion which killed 10
OL,6,FCriminal charges will be brought
OL,7,Fagainst the Government of Jersey over
OL,8,Fthe Haut du Mont flats explosion,
OL,9,Fwhich killed 10 people.
OL,11,FThe States Employment Board (SEB),
OL,12,Fwhich employs public servants, will
OL,13,Fface two charges under the island's
OL,14,FHealth and Safety at Work Law.
OL,16,FIt concerns the actions of the States
OL,17,Fof Jersey Fire and Rescue Service and
OL,18,Ftheir Emergency Services Control
OL,19,FCentre on Friday 9 December 2022, the
OL,20,Fnight before the fatal incident.
