OL,3,CGovernment faces criminal charges over
OL,4,Cexplosion which killed 10
OL,6,FThe Fire Service attended the block of
OL,7,Fflats in St Helier after residents
OL,8,Freported smelling gas.
OL,10,FThe following morning, just before
OL,11,F4am, there was a gas explosion.
OL,13,FThe charges are being brought against
OL,14,Fthe SEB as the employer, not any
OL,15,Findividual.
OL,17,FThe SEB is accused of failing to
OL,18,Fensure the health and safety of
OL,19,Femployees, and people not in their
OL,20,Femployment, including members of the
OL,21,Fpublic.
