OL,3,CGovernment faces criminal charges over
OL,4,Cexplosion which killed 10
OL,6,FIt follows an investigation by the
OL,7,FHealth and Safety Inspectorate (HSI),
OL,8,FJersey's independent regulator.
OL,10,FThe charges will be brought before
OL,11,FJersey Magistrate's Court on Thursday
OL,12,F25 September.
OL,14,FIf the alleged offences are proven,
OL,15,Fthe SEB could face unlimited fines.
