OL,3,CGovernment faces criminal charges over
OL,4,Cexplosion which killed 10
OL,6,FThe Board's Chair and Chief Minister,
OL,7,FDeputy Lyndon Farnham, says: "We
OL,8,Fremain committed to supporting the
OL,9,Fbereaved families and displaced
OL,10,Fresidents throughout the ongoing legal
OL,11,Fprocess, and we will continue to
OL,12,Fprovide that support for as long as it
OL,13,Fis needed.
OL,15,F"The Government is determined to learn
OL,16,Fall possible lessons from the Health
OL,17,Fand Safety Inspectorate investigation.
