OL,6,F"We are committed to ensuring that
OL,7,Fevery practical step is taken so that
OL,8,Fa tragedy of this nature can never
OL,9,Fhappen again."
OL,11,FThe victims' families have been
OL,12,Finformed of this development.
OL,14,FThe same two health and safety charges
OL,15,Fhave already been brought against
OL,16,FJersey Gas Company Ltd, which trades
OL,17,Funder the name Island Energy.
